---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { sitePath } from "../lib/sitePath";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Introduction"
  description="Undergraduate physics at IISER Bhopal — milestones and notes."
  wide
>
  <div class="home">
    <div class="intro-hero">
      <div class="intro-text">
        <h1>Introduction</h1>
        <p class="lede">
          Before I tell you more, let me tell you about the way I would like die.
          I want to die falling into a <b><i>black hole</i></b>. I would probably be spaghettified, but
          lets say I'm not. I just want to experience how it would feel to be dilated in time.
          A way to describe what I want to feel is <i><strong>infinity</strong></i>.
        </p>
      </div>
      <figure class="intro-visual">
        <img
          src={sitePath("/images/black-hole.jpg")}
          alt="Supermassive black hole at the center of galaxy M87 (Event Horizon Telescope)"
          width="560"
          height="560"
          loading="eager"
          decoding="async"
        />
        <figcaption>
          <a
            href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Black_hole_-_Messier_87_crop_max_res.jpg"
            rel="license noopener noreferrer"
            target="_blank"
          >M87*</a> · Event Horizon Telescope
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>

    <p class="intro-followup">
      Hi! I'm Saathvik Bogam, an undergraduate student at the Indian Institute of Science
      Education and Research, Bhopal. My interests lie in Physics and Mathematics, along
      with a bit of programming. I've made this website to track my academic journey
      , along with my notes for different core physics and mathematics courses. I also
      really enjoy philosophy and media analysis. My favourite pieces of fiction include 
      Steins;Gate, Sound! Euphonium and Land of the Lustrous, along with games like Hollow Knight.
      
    </p>

    <ul class="actions">
      <li><a href={sitePath("/journey/")}>Timeline of milestones</a></li>
      <li><a href={sitePath("/notes/")}>Notes</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .intro-hero {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr minmax(12rem, 16rem);
    gap: 2rem 2.5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .intro-text {
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .lede {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 42ch;
  }

  .intro-followup {
    margin: 2rem 0 0;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .intro-followup:empty {
    display: none;
  }

  .actions {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 2rem 0 0;
  }

  .actions li {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .actions a {
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .intro-visual {
    margin: 0;
    align-self: center;
  }

  .intro-visual img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 2px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 2rem rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
  }

  .intro-visual figcaption {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-align: center;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .intro-hero {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .intro-visual {
      max-width: 14rem;
      margin-inline: auto;
    }
  }
</style>
